ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 7th day of March, 2016, the Application for Leave to File a Reply is GRANTED, and the Petition for Extraordinary Relief Pursuant to King’s Bench Jurisdiction is DENIED.
Justice EAKIN did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
